      <title>泰国新总理皮查伊保留内阁成员，担任财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/new-thailand-pm-keeps-pichai-as-finance-chief-in-cabinet-line-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理巴东丹·西那瓦公布了新内阁阵容，保留皮猜担任财政部长，这一举动表明泰国在振兴东南亚第二大经济体的重任中将保持政策的连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/new-thailand-pm-keeps-pichai-as-finance-chief-in-cabinet-line-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 04:14:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普亲属在 X 上遭黑客攻击，发布虚假加密货币公告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trump-relatives-are-hacked-on-x-with-fake-crypto-announcement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，一些特朗普家族成员的社交媒体资料遭到入侵，以发布有关加密项目的虚假公告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trump-relatives-are-hacked-on-x-with-fake-crypto-announcement</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 03:02:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国服务业扩张放缓 显现经济疲软新迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/china-services-expansion-cools-in-new-sign-of-economic-weakness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项私人调查显示，中国服务业活动扩张低于预期，加剧了人们对经济健康状况的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/china-services-expansion-cools-in-new-sign-of-economic-weakness</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 01:51:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯誓言在逮捕陷入困境的前市长后迅速伸张正义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ex-philippine-mayor-tied-to-laundering-nabbed-in-indonesia-abs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯 (Ferdinand Marcos Jr.) 誓言要迅速解决针对一名前市长的洗钱和人口贩卖指控的案件。周三，该市长在印度尼西亚被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ex-philippine-mayor-tied-to-laundering-nabbed-in-indonesia-abs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 00:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
